## 🚀 **Next Steps**

The quality playbook is **production-ready**. To use it:

1. **Read AGENTS.md** — Bootstrap context for any AI session working on chi
2. **Run functional tests** — `go test ./quality -v` (expects 36 tests to pass)
3. **Apply code review protocol** — Use `quality/RUN_CODE_REVIEW.md` for any chi changes
4. **Run integration tests** — `quality/RUN_INTEGRATION_TESTS.md` for end-to-end validation
5. **Conduct spec audit** — Copy `quality/RUN_SPEC_AUDIT.md` prompt to Claude/GPT-4/Gemini for Council of Three results

